<h1>Accessibility Statement</h1>
<p>My aim for this website is to provide an experience that functions for the widest possible audience, regardless of technology or ability. It strives to conform to level AA compliance for the <a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG21/">Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.1</a>.</p>

<p>Issues with this site’s accessibility can be submitted as <a href="https://github.com/SparrowSpit/danielbivins-dot-com/issues">a GitHub issue</a>, or by <a href="mailto:dbivins☛REMOVE-THIS☚@protonmail.com?subject=Accessibility issue">emailing me directly</a>. These issues will be taken seriously and I will try to remedy the problem as quickly as time allows.</p>
